      "content": "hey, i saw something really weird on my way to work today and i cant stop thinking about it. there was this specific patch of sidewalk near the construction site where the concrete pattern just... repeated. like, the same crack and the same discoloration appeared exactly every three feet, like a texture that was tiled. it didnt look like a coincidence, it looked like a mistake. does that sound crazy or have u heard of stuff like that happening?",
